{"tid":260721,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Nokia 9再次現身　8GB RAM版本降臨 (00:10)","createTime":"2017-05-27T22:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T06:27:32.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7adc49d09518b2dc4139622a102aee960d76f1a8","tid":260721,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T22:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170528/img/20170528001010fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170528%2Fimg%2F20170528001010fi_p1.jpg&h=e93c3624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=weW6yIUZoGcZx37EmzOfSsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=b5219781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】外媒報道，早前HMD諾基亞新機跑分現身Geekbench跑分數據庫，該機應該就是Nokia 9，據當時的表格來看，這款手機搭載高通驍龍835處理器，內存為4GB。<br />\n<br />\n然而，在日前，Nokia 9再次出現在Geekbench數據庫中，與上次不同的是，這次的機器搭載的不是4GB內存，而是令人印象深刻的8GB，這意味着Nokia 9可能有不同內存大小的版本，目前來說，至少4GB內存版和8GB內存版這兩種是存在的。<br />\n<br />\n其他配置方面，Nokia 9將採用一塊分辨率為1440*2540的顯示屏，搭載雙攝像頭，具有3.5毫米耳機插孔和USB Type-C接口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170528/20170528001010fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170528%2F20170528001010fi.html&d=weW6yIUZoGcZx37EmzOfSsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=dcc96b99\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170528/20170528001010fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"b2003658f4be38129bd80d012bb9a5e817b0cbb0","tid":260721,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T00:21:22.000Z","msg":"行iOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77fb1fcd10f212f45cf5d4a1350213390c14a85","tid":260721,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"nokia機變咗都市傳說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d2457c455de8126ab3622cd388f1f853ec1cae","tid":260721,"uid":54104,"l